     <text:p text:style-name="P26"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/O_scrisoare_pierdut#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T9"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">n epoca Scrisorii pierdute, se vota pe colegii censitare. Cetenii erau mprii, pe criterii social-economice, n trei categorii. Majoritatea nu puteau vota dect indirect, prin delegai</text:span></text:p>
